Interface ShortStack

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Stack<Short>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractShortBigList, AbstractShortBigList.ShortSubList, AbstractShortList, AbstractShortList.ShortSubList, AbstractShortStack, ShortArrayList, ShortBigArrayBigList, ShortBigLists.ListBigList, ShortBigLists.Singleton, ShortLists.Singleton
    public interface ShortStack
extends Stack<Short>
    A type-specific Stack; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.
